     * root that contains a list of repository and tag names mapped to layer IDs.
     *
     * ```json
     * {
     * "hello-world": {
     * "latest": "565a9d68a73f6706862bfe8409a7f659776d4d60a8d096eb4a3cbce6999cc2a1"
     * }
     * }
     * ```
